# Next.js + Bun Project Rules

## Development Commands
- Use `bun run dev` for development
- Use `bun run build` for production build
- Use `bun run start` for production server

## Code Style
- Always use TypeScript
- Use 'use client' directive for client components
- Use @ alias for imports (@/lib, @/components, @/types)
- Follow Next.js 15 App Router conventions

## Database
- PostgreSQL via postgres.js
- Environment variables in .env.local
- Never commit .env.local to git

